'''沙棘'''（學名：''Hippophae rhamnoides''），或作'''海沙棘'''<ref name="Foldesi">{{Cite journal|title=Sea Buckthorn ( Hippophae rhamnoides L.):: A Promising New Medicinal and Food Crop|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1300/J044v01n01_04|last=Bernáth|first=J.|last2=Földesi|first2=D.|date=1992-07-13|journal=Journal of Herbs, Spices & Medicinal Plants|issue=1-2|doi=10.1300/J044v01n01_04|volume=1|pages=27–35|language=en|issn=1049-6475|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216005107/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1300/J044v01n01_04|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[沙棘屬|沙棘屬]]的一種帶有棘刺的落葉灌木，原產於亞洲和歐洲的溫帶、寒溫帶地區<ref name="Li">{{Cite journal|title=Sea Buckthorn (Hippophae rhamnoides L.): A Multipurpose Plant|url=https://journals.ashs.org/view/journals/horttech/6/4/article-p370.xml|last=Li|first=Thomas S.C.|last2=Schroeder|first2=W.R.|date=1996-10|journal=HortTechnology|issue=4|doi=10.21273/HORTTECH.6.4.370|volume=6|pages=370–380|issn=1063-0198}}</ref>。沙棘可防風固沙，其果實可以食用或用來製作飲料，此外沙棘果在美容和藥用上也有價值。

== 形態 ==
[[File:Seabuckthorn_berries,_Nubra_valley,_Ladakh.jpg|thumb]]

作為一種落葉灌木，沙棘的高度在二米至四米之間<ref name="Li" />，枝幹粗糙、外皮呈黑色<ref name="Li" />，葉披針形<ref name="Synge">{{cite book|last1=Synge|first1=PM|title=Dictionary of gardening: A practical and scientific encyclopaedia of horticulture|date=1974|publisher=Clarendon Press|location=Oxford|edition=2|isbn=978-0198691068}}</ref>。在種下三年後開花<ref name="Foldesi" />，雌雄異株，通過風來傳播種子<ref name="Li" />。

單個果實重量在270至480毫克之間，富含維生素C、E、[[维生素B12|B12]]<ref name="Stobdan">{{Cite journal|title=Attributes of Seabuckthorn (Hippophae rhamnoides L.) to Meet Nutritional Requirements in High Altitude.|url=http://publications.drdo.gov.in/ojs/index.php/dsj/article/view/344|last=Stobdan|first=Tsering|last2=Chaurasia|first2=Om Prakash|date=2010-03-29|journal=Defence Science Journal|issue=2|doi=10.14429/dsj.60.344|volume=60|pages=226–230|last3=Korekar|first3=Girish|last4=Yadav|first4=Ashish|last5=Singh|first5=Shashi}}</ref>和類胡蘿蔔素、類黃酮和脂肪酸<ref name="Bal">{{Cite journal|title=Sea buckthorn berries: A potential source of valuable nutrients for nutraceuticals and cosmoceuticals|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0963996911001591|last=Bal|first=Lalit M.|last2=Meda|first2=Venkatesh|date=2011-08-01|journal=Food Research International|issue=7|doi=10.1016/j.foodres.2011.03.002|series=Exotic Fruits: their Composition, Nutraceutical and Agroindustrial Potential|volume=44|pages=1718–1727|language=en|issn=0963-9969|last3=Naik|first3=S. N.|last4=Satya|first4=Santosh|access-date=2021-03-05|archive-date=2016-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108234545/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0963996911001591|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===共生菌===
沙棘的根系十分發達，而且當植株成長至一至兩年，其根會開始長出含[[弗兰克氏菌属|弗兰克氏菌]]（''[[Frankia|Frankia]]''，屬[[放線菌門|放線菌門]]）的[[固氮作用|固氮]]共生菌<ref name="Stewart">{{Cite journal|title=Nodulation and nitrogen-fixation byHippophaë rhamnoides L. in the field|url=https://doi.org/10.1007/BF01880184|last=Stewart|first=W. D. P.|last2=Pearson|first2=M. C.|date=1967-04-01|journal=Plant and Soil|issue=2|doi=10.1007/BF01880184|volume=26|pages=348–360|language=en|issn=1573-5036}}</ref><ref name="Gatner">{{Cite journal|title=Observations on the fine structure of the root nodule endophyte of Hippophaë rhamnoides L.|url=https://doi.org/10.1007/BF00407709|last=Gatner|first=E. M. S.|last2=Gardner|first2=I. C.|date=1970-09-01|journal=Archiv für Mikrobiologie|issue=3|doi=10.1007/BF00407709|volume=70|pages=183–196|language=en|issn=1432-072X}}</ref><ref name="Lu">{{Cite journal|title=Seabuckthorn: a multipurpose plant species for fragile mountains|url=https://agris.fao.org/agris-search/search.do?recordID=XF2015037660|last=Rongsen|first=L.|last2=International Centre for Integrated Mountain Development|first2=Kathmandu (Nepal) eng 165171|date=1992}}</ref>。因著這層關係，種植有沙棘的土壤都含豐富氮肥。共生菌的固氮活動速率並不固定，會受外間天氣或額外氮肥的施與而影響<ref name="Stewart" /><ref name="Montpetit">{{Cite journal|title=In vitro propagation and subsequent nodulation of the actinorhizal Hippophae rhamnoides L.|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/BF00033643|last=Montpetit|first=D.|last2=Lalonde|first2=M.|date=1988|journal=Plant Cell, Tissue and Organ Culture|issue=3|doi=10.1007/BF00033643|volume=15|pages=189–199|language=en|issn=0167-6857}}</ref>。

